e":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T15:44:34.000Z","msg":"佢啲詞真係幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日諗點樣可以揀啲咁啱嘅字填落去"},{"pid":"eda60eedc7d146cdfcb70ca34f4b5ef0de8b72d2","tid":2382984,"uid":17335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b7677e9e5c091baba4f43420c3a4b0c2199447a6","tid":2382984,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T15:26:42.000Z","msg":"其實佢身世都幾慘<br />\n老公死咗 個國家又打仗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T16:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老公冷落，被遺棄，老公死，國家廢<br />\n李清照仲要被結婚，自力離婚<br />\n都唔少人白眼佢，好彩佢自己有才學"},{"pid":"10549bf9d0508f1355e85e8f732e31273bc0d7aa","tid":2382984,"uid":21141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T16:11:27.000Z","msg":"好凄慘既女人<br />\n中年個陣先國破家亡，仲要撞正最恥辱既靖康之難，一個女人係果個年代四處漂泊，再婚完又離婚收場，仲要搞到上公堂差啲坐監，被娘家唾棄<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b73012d40888f798bdee8ac085d506b68ba47e","tid":2382984,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T16:27:16.000Z","msg":"呢個po 好熟口面<br />\n係唔係開過一次<br />\n<br />\n定係格式相似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d00c7651996699407c7fb135d3905d5a5781707","tid":2382984,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T17:16:07.000Z","msg":"點解冇人拍劇講葉紹袁三個女？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2345625\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2345625</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓主會唔會講吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ef3724ad0ba7d151cf1463246fd4d8a78f97c4","tid":2382984,"uid":302951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":