"古人對文字嘅運用真係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別去到呢種史上留名大師級<br />\n今時今日，係精緻方面真係好難超越"},{"pid":"dde1329a28395d5ed789be748822607450bf24cb","tid":2382984,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10549bf9d0508f1355e85e8f732e31273bc0d7aa","tid":2382984,"uid":21141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T16:11:27.000Z","msg":"好凄慘既女人<br />\n中年個陣先國破家亡，仲要撞正最恥辱既靖康之難，一個女人係果個年代四處漂泊，再婚完又離婚收場，仲要搞到上公堂差啲坐監，被娘家唾棄<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />晚年想收個女弟子傳功<br />\n結果被人哋阿媽話，唔好痴埋去呢種人"},{"pid":"e207c398faf941fe0323d7cd98c50fd4995cdf5c","tid":2382984,"uid":11237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:25:15.000Z","msg":"如果覺得李清照既人生經歷慘<br />\n我諗同時亦係覺得當時既好多女人都好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n家破人亡，唔只李清照一人如此<br />\n只係佢有才學可以表達內心感受，幾多人做唔到<br />\n但同時佢有一身才學，反而又係佢最可憐可惜之處<br />\n<br />\n可能當年無才學、無情懷，就可以無遇上趙明誠<br />\n可能佢無才學、無情懷，面對呢種愁時<br />\n反可以好似無才無德既普通女人咁，咕一聲吞左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢啲詞係好靚"},{"pid":"fa6560853e1bdcbffa466cb6a2590c616b9def94","tid":2382984,"uid":204227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:25:43.000Z","msg":"2019年8月31號，香港警察係太子站<br />\n＆黨鐵車箱入面無差別攻擊市民<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EHDW1rq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEHDW1rq.png&h=51c9b0ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gkn8Sym.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgkn8Sym.jpg&h=43931c2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wfXHW0p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwfXHW0p.png&h=86c2b8eb&s={SIZE}\" /><